http://www.isid.org

Date: Fri 9 Aug 2013
Source: Boletin Integrado de Vigilancia Epidemiologica (Ministerio de Salud de la Nacion, Argentina) Reporte Epidemiologico de Cordoba [in Spanish, trans., edited]


Cutaneous anthrax surveillance
-----------------------------
Source: Sistema Nacional de Vigilancia de la Salud (SNVS) [National Health Surveillance System] - Modules C2 & SIVILA [Sistema de Vigilancia de Laboratorio/Laboratory Surveillance System]. Notifications include suspects, probables, confirmed, and discarded cases.

Table 1: Notified and confirmed cases by province and region, Argentina. Years 2012-2013, up until week 27 [week of 1 Jul 2013].

2012
----
Province / Notified / Confirmed
Buenos Aires [Centro] / 2 / 0
Santa Fe [Centro] / 1 / 0
Total Centro Region / 3 / 0
Mendoza [Cuyo] / 0 / 0
Total Cuyo Region / 0 / 0
Corrientes [NEA] / 2 / 1
Total NEA [Northeast] Region / 2 / 1
Tierra del Fuego [Sur] / 1 / 0
Total Sur Region / 1 / 0
Total Argentina / 6 / 1

2013
----
Province / Notified / Confirmed
Buenos Aires [Centro] / 7 / 3
Santa Fe [Centro] / 2 / 0
Total Centro Region / 9 / 3
Mendoza [Cuyo] / 1 / 0
Total Cuyo Region / 1 / 0
Corrientes [NEA] / 0 / 0
Total NEA [Northeast] Region / 0 / 0
Tierra del Fuego [Sur] / 1 / 0
Total Sur Region / 1 / 0
Total Argentina / 11 / 3

